      "books": "From the Battlefield to the White House to the Boardroom: Leading Organizations to Values-Based Results",
      "books-href": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/51484111-from-the-battlefield-to-the-white-house-to-the-boardroom",
      "Title": "From the Battlefield to the White House to the Boardroom: Leading Organizations to Values-Based Results",
